'''Lommy''', called '''Lommy Greenhands''', is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first]] and [[Season 2|second]] seasons. He was played by guest star [[Eros Vlahos]] and debuted in &quot;[[Fire and Blood]].&quot; Lommy is killed by [[Polliver]] while traveling north on the Kingsroad as a recruit in the [[Night's Watch]].

